sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Registry
    participant SessionLauncher
    participant DesktopAgent
    participant MCPTool
    participant RDSH as RDSH Session<br/>(agent_user_N)

    Note over Registry: Startup
    Registry->>SessionLauncher: --user agent_user_1 --exe GoogleSearchMcp.exe --args "--urls :5001"
    SessionLauncher->>RDSH: CreateProcessAsUser (MCPTool)
    Registry->>SessionLauncher: --user agent_user_1 --exe desktop_agent.exe --args "--port 8001 --mcp-url :5001"
    SessionLauncher->>RDSH: CreateProcessAsUser (DesktopAgent)
    Registry->>DesktopAgent: GET /health
    DesktopAgent-->>Registry: 200 OK
    Note over Registry: Slot 1 ready

    Note over Client: Task Execution
    Client->>Registry: GET /session/acquire?agent_type=desktop
    Registry-->>Client: { agent_url: ":8001", slot: 1 }

    Client->>DesktopAgent: POST /run { "task": "Open notepad and type Hello" }
    DesktopAgent->>MCPTool: MCP initialize
    MCPTool-->>DesktopAgent: session ID + capabilities
    DesktopAgent->>MCPTool: tools/list
    MCPTool-->>DesktopAgent: [open_notepad_and_type, google_search]
    DesktopAgent->>DesktopAgent: LangGraph invokes tool
    DesktopAgent->>MCPTool: open_notepad_and_type("Hello")
    MCPTool->>RDSH: Launch Notepad
    MCPTool->>RDSH: FlaUI attach + SendKeys
    MCPTool->>RDSH: CopyFromScreen → base64 PNG
    RDSH-->>MCPTool: screenshot base64
    MCPTool-->>DesktopAgent: base64 PNG
    DesktopAgent->>DesktopAgent: Extract screenshot from ToolMessage
    DesktopAgent-->>Client: { result: "done", screenshot_base64: "..." }

    Client->>Registry: POST /session/release/8001?agent_type=desktop
    Registry-->>Client: { released: 8001 }
    Note over Registry: Slot 1 marked available

    Note over Registry: Health Check Loop (every 30s)
    Registry->>DesktopAgent: GET /health
    alt healthy
        DesktopAgent-->>Registry: 200 OK
    else unhealthy
        Registry->>DesktopAgent: terminate
        Registry->>SessionLauncher: relaunch slot
    end